    crawlercommons.domains.EffectiveTldFinder.EffectiveTLD.isWild()
    since 1.6 - replaced by EffectiveTldFinder.EffectiveTLD.isWildcard()
    crawlercommons.robots.BaseRobotsParser.parseContent​(String, byte[], String, String)
    since 1.4 - replaced by BaseRobotsParser.parseContent(java.lang.String,byte[],java.lang.String,java.util.Collection<java.lang.String>). Passing a collection of robot names gives users more control how user-agent and robot names are matched. Passing a list of names is also more efficient as it does not require to split the robot name string again and again on every robots.txt file to be parsed.
    crawlercommons.robots.SimpleRobotRulesParser.parseContent​(String, byte[], String, String)
